title: 4th Movement: Occult Warfare
description:
1. Casta de Guerreros con Fuego (0:00 - 6:23)

The spirit?s the guide when darkness is upon men.
Nobility will be our nature. Following the code of honor;
living by virtues: sacrifice, defending our kin,
defending freedom, to always see good over ill.
Impel men to overcome; let no kinfolk go to Hel.
Courage of the creed of stone.
Glorifying the Hall of Fallen Warriors scarred from battle,
for they swore oaths -- which they never break --
to the Chief of Combat. Gathered on sacred ground
around him and his sword.
Go forth into fight, and victory we will have.
When danger is nigh, we will not react with fear but with anger.
Crush the source of all evils. Bind them in the light;
only the noble will rule. Elite inducers of justice by the Folk Law.
United, we will stand. His father pursues wisdom,
he pursues vigor. Together, salute the strong,
bringing men to worthy deed; to honor and righteous striving.
Sky-high into well being,
the four tongues of the sun
with the sword's motion toward what is to come.
There is no equal; we praise by merit.
